<p>
This is a task/goal manager built using SQLite and Node.js. The server uses the
Express framework with Handlebars for templating.  In the future I aim to
provide easy import/export of todo.txt files and visualization of your tasks.
</p>
<p>Note:
    <em>
    This is a DEVELOPMENT deployment. Guest accounts <b>expire</b> after one
    day, Registered accounts may be reset <b>without notice</b> or migrated 
    into oblivion. Use the <b>download</b> function to save your lists.
    </em>
</p>

