<h2>Working Features</h2>
<ul>
    <li>CLI and web interface</li>
    <li>Tasks: Create, Delete, Mark Done</li>
    <li>Tasks: filter by text (e.g. only tasks with "+work")
    <li>Import/Export: todo.txt format</li>
</ul>
</p>
